25:25.940 --> 25:28.568
There's something
about the notion of an infinite circle

25:28.650 --> 25:30.277
that fascinates me.

25:30.570 --> 25:31.605
Oh.

25:32.490 --> 25:35.357
The hangman's noose is a circle

25:35.450 --> 25:38.237
