26:17.450 --> 26:19.315
Not till the water's over my head.

26:22.040 --> 26:23.689
I know it'll be the death of me.

26:28.290 --> 26:31.282
Gray waters, dark with mud,

26:31.380 --> 26:33.371
things swimmin' blindly in it.

26:34.760 --> 26:36.830
