53:29.620 --> 53:32.202
Shouldn't have elderly slaves
on their feet all day.

53:35.580 --> 53:37.127
Needn't worry yourself, madam.

53:37.210 --> 53:38.620
He earns a fair wage for his work.

53:38.710 --> 53:40.541
Isn't that right, Eutroclus?

53:40.630 --> 53:42.586
Yes, I do, Captain.

53:42.970 --> 53:44.540
You mean to say that you're free?

53:45.260 --> 53:46.466
Yes, madam.

53:46.550 --> 53:48.006
He used to be my slave.

53:48.100 --> 53:51.092
Till one day I fell asleep
with the lamp still burning.

53:51.180 --> 53:54.593
The cabin caught fire
and Troklus pulled me out in time.

53:54.850 --> 53:56.647
After that,
I petitioned a court for his release

53:56.730 --> 53:58.015
on the grounds of meritorious service

53:58.110 --> 54:00.351
and offered a surety for his freedom.

54:01.070 --> 54:04.392
Been working for me ever since.
Best waterman on the river.

54:10.080 --> 54:12.867
You must be grateful
every day for What he's done for you.

54:24.260 --> 54:26.125
Keep your eye up river.

54:26.220 --> 54:28.711
You'll want to steer around any logs.

54:28.970 --> 54:31.712
All right, lad.
It's your turn at the pole.

54:32.430 --> 54:34.478
This is harder than it looks.

54:35.230 --> 54:37.687
The current is stronger than I imagined.

54:38.900 --> 54:41.266
Will you join me, Sassenach?

54:44.610 --> 54:45.986
Of course.

55:00.920 --> 55:02.410
Well, What's this?

55:05.550 --> 55:06.710
A present.

55:11.010 --> 55:12.170
Open it.

55:34.580 --> 55:35.649
Do ye like it?

55:40.380 --> 55:41.779
Oh, Jamie.

55:44.500 --> 55:45.876
It's wonderful.

55:51.050 --> 55:52.847
Where did you find it?

55:53.470 --> 55:54.801
I saw the box when I--

55:54.890 --> 55:57.131
When I went to the goldsmith
to have the ruby set.

55:57.230 --> 55:58.766
Oh, my God.

56:01.020 --> 56:02.226
It's a microscope.

56:03.060 --> 56:04.186
Aye.

56:08.030 --> 56:12.273
And, perhaps, one day,
