56:35.180 --> 56:36.716
Brianna, for one.

56:38.680 --> 56:40.477
I gave the pearls to her.

56:42.310 --> 56:44.107
They're an heirloom, after all.

56:47.110 --> 56:49.146
And this ring is all I need.

56:50.990 --> 56:53.231
Twenty-four years ago
I married ye, Sassenach.

56:55.870 --> 56:58.327
